## Usage

Check https://github.com/gefeiZ/sc_var/tree/main/Vignettes for details



Data request: 

Single cell data &

Peak co-accessibility Data or Peak to gene linkage Data (which could obtained from single cell data using cicero or signac) &

GWAS data 


